Message.message: ...your delicious memories, Leonardo! I must feast on them!...
[Memory] I recall slaving over the commission for Santa Maria at the workshop. My exhaustion was such that I could scarcely focus on the canvas before me.
[Memory] I had awoken suddenly in my cot. The studio was as black as pitch but I'd become aware of the presence of an unknown person in the room with me.
...return to me at once, Leonardo! You are fat with recollection!...
[Memory] I lay, terrified, my eyes straining in vain to penetrate the inky darkness and identify the intruder. Then, suddenly, I was being lifted against my will, but by no corporeal hand!
...I can practically taste those juicy memories, dripping as they are with such significance. Come to me! I promise there will be no pain. No, no physical pain at all...
[Transmission] ...my first is in nothing and also in nowhere...
[Transmission] ...my second's in reserve but somehow it's in there...
